Dalgona Coffee

INGREDIENTS : 

coffee powder 
sugar
Warm water
Ice cubes 
Milk 

add 2 tablespoon of coffee poweder, sugar, warm water in a bowl.
take a whip or and electric mixer and mix till it is foam / creamy.
in a cup, add cold milk, and ice and add the mixture on top of your milk.
if needed add some sugar and ice just incase!
(* the mixture should be floating on your milk for best reesults)